      • getPageContext

        public String getPageContext()
        Context (GuidanceHelper.CONTEXT) is used to describe the page/tool that is being used in this helper. Context is the main title (ex. matrix or wizard name) and context 2 is used for the subtitle (ex. matrix cell or wizard page). If left blank, then nothing displays on the page.
        Returns:

      • getPageContext2

        public String getPageContext2()
        Context2 (GuidanceHelper.CONTEXT2) is used to describe the page/tool that is being used in this helper. Context is the main title (ex. matrix or wizard name) and Context2 is used for the subtitle (ex. matrix cell or wizard page). If left blank, then nothing displays on the page.
        Returns:
